            "fieldname": "help_html",
            "fieldtype": "HTML",
            "label": "Help",
            "options": "<div style='padding:16px;background:#f8f9fa;border-radius:8px'><h4>📖 How to Use</h4><p>After saving your API key, go to: <b><a href='/ai-architect'>/ai-architect</a></b></p><p>Or press <kbd>Ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>Shift</kbd>+<kbd>A</kbd> from anywhere in Frappe.</p><h5 style='margin-top:16px'>Example Commands:</h5><ul><li><code>Create a DocType \"Task\" with fields: title, assigned_to, priority, due_date</code></li><li><code>Add a currency field \"budget\" to Project</code></li><li><code>Create a workflow for Leave Application: Draft → Approved → Rejected</code></li></ul><h5 style='margin-top:16px'>Troubleshooting:</h5><ul><li><b>Quota exceeded?</b> Add more keys in \"API Key Failover\" tab</li><li><b>Invalid key?</b> Check at <a href='https://aistudio.google.com/apikey' target='_blank'>Google AI Studio</a></li><li><b>Permission error?</b> Check \"Allowed Roles\" in Safety tab</li></ul></div>"
        }
